Ar Creates an ar archive.
Ar.ArFileSet This is a FileSet with the option to specify permissions and other attributes.
Ar.ArLongFileMode Set of options for long file handling in the task.
ArEntry This class represents an entry in an Ar archive.
ArOutputStream The ArOutputStream writes an ar archive as an OutputStream.
ArUtils This class provides static utility methods to work with byte streams.
